How to make Mediterranean chicken with pan-fried veggies and tzatziki üôå

Macros per serve:
55g protein
17g fat
76g carbs

673 calories per serve üí™

Cooking settings üë®‚Äçüç≥
Oven: Bake at 200¬∞C (400¬∞F) for 20‚Äì25 minutes, flipping halfway.
Air Fryer: Cook at 200¬∞C (400¬∞F) for 12‚Äì15 minutes, flipping halfway.

Ingredients for 3 servings ‚¨áÔ∏è

For the chicken:
700g Chicken Thigh Fillets
3 Tbsp Greek Yoghurt
Few Sprigs of Fresh Dill
2 cloves of Garlic
1 Tsp Paprika
1 Tsp Cumin
1 Lemon
Salt & Pepper

For the pan-fried veggies:
1 Red Pepper
1 Yellow Pepper
1 Courgette
1/2 Red Onion

For the yoghurt sauce:
5 Tbsp Greek Yoghurt
1/2 Cucumber
Few Sprigs of Fresh Dill
1 Lemon

Also:
1 Cups Uncooked Rice
